    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's perfect if you're looking for a reliable, smooth journey without that brand-new price tag. I've taken great care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles! Let's get you on the road.",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
