      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and has undergone a recent valve clearance adjustment to maintain peak volumetric efficiency. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, sending power to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue, and the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled for timing reliability. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance characteristic of this chassis. A well-sorted driver's car for the purist.",
